! array frustration = frustration|grievance|disappointment|disappointed|dissatisfaction|disgruntlement|letdown|setback
! array guilt = guilt|guilty|blame|disgrace|liability|regret|remorse|shame|crime|error|failing|infamy|lapse|misconduct|offense|selfreproach|slip|transgression|wickedness|wrong
