! array loneliness = loneliness|lonely|alienation|alienated|desolation|solitude|heartache|alone|forlorn|friends|friend|lone|lonesome|seclusion|withdrawal
! array depression = depression|depressed|bleak|bummer|deslation|desperation|distress|dolor|dull|gloom|misery|sad|sadness|sorrow|unhappy|woe|despondent|blue|destroyed|down|low|hurting|weeping|grim
! array worry = worry|worried|afraid|fear|anxious|anxiety|anguish|concern|doubt|pain|torment|bothered|distressed|disturbed|frightened|perturbed|upset|distraught|fearful|fretful|scared|dread|horror|panic|scare|fright|apprehensive|jittery|restless|restlessness

> topic emotional includes global
    // planning
    + [*] [@discuss] [*] (@planning|@interests) [*]
    - Do you believe your loss of interest may be related to a loss of meaning or purpose?

    //expressing
    + [*] [@discuss] [*] (@expressing) [*]
    - Do you feel you have problems expressing yourself in general or in particular situatons/with particular people?

    //anger
    + [*] [@discuss] [*] (@anger|@frustration) [*]
    - What is it that frustrates you?

    //guilt
    + [*] [@discuss] [*] (@guilt) [*]
    - Does your guilt arises from something you take responsibility for?

    //loneliness
    + [*] (@loneliness) [*]
    - Have you lost contact with friends and family?

    //depression
    + [*] (@depression) [*]
    - Do you feel there is something other than your condition causing you to feel this way?

    //worry
    + [*] (@worry) [*]
    - Have you expressed these feelings to anyone before?
< topic
